These are Puzzles for 4x7 Level 2

.:: Puzzle 4x7-Level-2-1::.
There are 7 different favourite beverages: almond-milk, mirinda, hot-chocolate, iced-tea, lemonade, milk, water
There are 7 different nationalities: italian, turkish, colombian, argentine, american, brazilian, nigerian
The people prefer 7 different types of sport: soccer, badminton, water-polo, handball, parkour, weightlifting, ice-hockey
The people use 7 different means of transport: scooter, skateboard, snowmobile, airplane, taxi, boat, helicopter
 1. the person who's sport is handball is on the far right##1
 2. the person who's sport is parkour is the argentine##1
 3. the person driving the taxi is the person who's sport is water-polo##1
 4. the turkish is on the left of the person driving the boat##1
 5. the italian is on the right of the nigerian##1
 6. the person drinking mirinda is the person who's sport is water-polo##1
 7. the person driving the helicopter is on the right of the american##1
 8. the person driving the airplane is between the person driving the helicopter and the brazilian##2
 9. the american is on the right of the person driving the snowmobile##1
10. the person drinking hot-chocolate is in the middle##1
11. the person who's sport is soccer is the person drinking lemonade##1
12. the person drinking lemonade is the person driving the scooter##1
13. the person drinking almond-milk is on the left of the colombian##1
14. the brazilian is the person driving the snowmobile##1
15. the person driving the boat is on the left of the nigerian##1
16. the person drinking mirinda is on the left of the person drinking milk##1
17. the person who's sport is weightlifting is on the left of the colombian##1
18. the person drinking water is on the right of the american##1
19. the person who's sport is ice-hockey is on the right of the person driving the skateboard##1

.:: Answer ::.
